{
  "name": "Hidden Building Pieces",
  "author": "AgentKush",
  "version": "2.8.0",
  "description": "Unlocks 54 hidden diagonal and curved building pieces for Concrete, Glass, Clay Brick, Stone, Scoria, Tempered Glass, Scoria Brick, Stone Brick, and Ice. ALSO adds 9 missing standard Ice building pieces (Wall, Floor, Ramp, Wall Angle, Beam, Roof Corner, Roof Half Pitch, Stairs, Floor Trapdoor). Adds missing Mesh_Ice_Kit (fixes ice building placement), fixes Ice_Wall_Curved type bug. All pieces can be repaired. Craft at appropriate benches (Ice is hand-craftable).",
